## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (Browser)
1. Open the app at `http://localhost:5173`
2. Click the dark mode toggle (top header, moon/sun icon)
3. Navigate to **Dashboard** — verify cards, chart area, notification card, action buttons all look clean
4. Navigate to **Patients** — verify table rows, patient detail sidebar, filter bar all have proper contrast
5. Navigate to **Appointments** — verify calendar grid cells, Quick Add form, Web Requests cards
6. Navigate to **Calendar** — verify calendar has proper dark background and no light stranded colors
7. Navigate to **Inventory** — verify table, filter chips, summary cards, AI sidebar popup
8. Toggle back to **light mode** — verify nothing broke

### Acceptance Criteria
- No "white islands" (light-colored elements left untouched in dark mode)
- Background hierarchy clearly visible: page `zinc-950` < card `zinc-900` < input `zinc-800`
- Text hierarchy: headlines `zinc-50`, body `zinc-200`, muted `zinc-400/500`
- All interactive states (hover, active, focus) have visible dark variants
